Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.67,0:00:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please keep the room bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.13,0:00:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.21,0:00:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.52,0:00:20.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My name is Seishiro Kurausu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:21.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have retired as a butler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:24.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and now live as a plantation owner in Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.36,0:00:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I have yet to retire!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be a Sanzenin butler to the very end!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.68,0:00:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing left for you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.38,0:00:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And a replacement for Himegami's \Nbeen found already,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.63,0:00:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm sure you've got no regrets left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.96,0:00:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could a beast know of my feelings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doesn't it bother you more \Nthat the beast is talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.02,0:00:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like even that \Npoverty-stricken butler
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.09,0:00:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will be able to manage \Nthe spoiled little miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.95,0:00:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! As if I could leave it in \Nthe hands of that greenhorn!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going back to Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.99,0:00:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, you aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to enjoy the rest of \Nyour days here in Brazil with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.11,0:00:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.69,0:01:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama! So it was you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:08.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So it's a dream punch line \Nright off the bat this week?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.97,0:01:11.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, then, good-bye, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way a tiger would talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:19.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Brazil Overseas Trips for Seniors
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.53,0:01:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Coffee plantation owner wanted in Brazil"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.86,0:01:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did this get into my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:36.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whosoever commands the \Nbutlers, commands the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:40.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Great Butler War that will \Nshake up the world has just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Klaus" is written as "kura" \Nas in "kurashiki (warehouse)"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.68,0:01:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and "usu" as in "usu-kine \N(mortar and pounder)"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am 100% Japanese!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:49.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Zettai nante shinjinai!\NI don't believe in absolutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:52.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukanou nante nai!\NNo such thing as impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:58.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirai wa hiraku te no naka ni aru\NThe future is in the open palm of my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:02:03.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dou yattemo katenai akuma ga\NA demon that I just can't win against
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.51,0:02:08.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Megami no kao o shite chakkari (O_O;)\NBrazenly pretending to be a goddess (O_O;)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:13.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Keikenchi ja tannai kurai dakara\NExperience points are almost not enough
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.36,0:02:19.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Isshou tanren shikou-sakugo ni sessa-takuma\NTraining for life, working hard at trial and error
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:24.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mondai nara muzukashii-hodo ude ga naru shi\NTougher the problem the more it gets me going
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:29.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yorokobu kao ga mirerya sore de ii shi\NSeeing the joy on your face is enough for me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:35.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Takara no chizu o boku wa te ni ireta\NI've found a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:41.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuou-mujin kimi o tsurete tsuki-susumou!\NTotally free, I'll take you and push forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:44.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Happii na kanchigai\NA happy misunderstanding
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:47.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikai wa yuruganai!\NMy pledge will stand fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:52.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaze no yukue mo kaete-miseru\NI'll even change the direction of the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:55.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakkou wa kini-shinai\NI won't care how I look
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.40,0:02:58.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Unmei ja kujikenai!\NNo destiny will discourage me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:03.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ano kumo chirasu hayate no gotoku!\NLike the sudden gale scattering the clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus is Japanese Because His \NName Is Written "Kurausu"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.31,0:03:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A good temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.14,0:03:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ironing out the morning paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is the butler's first \Nduty of the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, the delayed \Nrelease of "Dragon Quest"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.99,0:03:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is affecting the price of the stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think I had become a coffee \Nplantation owner, comfortably retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a strange dream I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to retire, why don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavens, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.42,0:04:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to spend the rest of my \Ndays at the Sanzenin household!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was merely speaking \Nof what I had dreamed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Freud, dreams embody \Nyour unconscious desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the depths of your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.91,0:04:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you are thinking you are tired \Nalready and want to retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I am not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if I were to leave, \Nthe Sanzenin household would...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...have no problem whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate and Maria will take \Ncare of the day-to-day things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.36,0:04:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no need to worry about \Nasset management and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.43,0:04:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially with the recent IT-related stocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's probably beyond your abilities already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must not run. I must not run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I must not run. I must not run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Mr. Klaus?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An AT Field! An emotional barrier, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.30,0:04:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I don't know anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:05:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could have gotten into Mr. \NKlaus? He seems so depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.99,0:05:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, something must have come \Nas a great shock to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.72,0:05:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:09.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim for a Space Legacy?!\NMahal
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea. Though, I did tell \Nhim that he could quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have to take \Nhis dream seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.66,0:05:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, if you have a butler who \Nhas served you for many years...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You give them a room of \Ntheir own at the residence
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and treat them like family...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have come as a \Nshock to be told to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.64,0:05:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he'd quit \Nover something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deep inside, you must adore \NMr. Klaus very much, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.12,0:05:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's just an easy character to mess with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then please don't tell him to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.06,0:05:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He may be getting swallowed up \Nin Dirac's sea right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then go do an involuntary \Nsalvage operation or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.25,0:05:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that laugh for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head Butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.51,0:06:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Maria, the Miss has \Ngiven me some time off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.33,0:06:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will spend the rest of my life in Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please! There's no way the Miss \Nseriously wants you to quit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But! But!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've made up your mind, \Nthen it cannot be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.42,0:06:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.24,0:06:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall inform the Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.36,0:06:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! There may be some sense \Nto what the Miss says, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dreaming of retirement...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.58,0:06:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I have become less than \Ndedicated without realizing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.41,0:06:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am thinking of going back to my days
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I was a footman aspiring \Nto become a butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A footman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:36.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Footmen are people who work under butlers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:39.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Incidentally, there are no footmen \Nin the Sanzenin household.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.78,0:06:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a footman, I challenge Hayate \NAyasaki to a serving-the-Miss match!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a way to stack the \Nodds against yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Butting in needlessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was almost on my way to \NBrazil, just as I'd planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A serving-the-Miss match?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recall asking you to \Ndo anything so bothersome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Mr. Klaus who suggested it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have certainly grown a lot \Nin a short amount of time, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you have one fatal flaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What about me is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's how you look too \Ngood when you cross-dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.56,0:07:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, a butler is ultimately \Nhis mistress's shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are too aware of \Nyourself as a protagonist!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he {\i1}is{\i0} actually the protagonist, \Nso it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, he is rather unassuming \Nfor a protagonist...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.26,0:07:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that supposed to be a compliment?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-At any rate, for the next 24 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we will wield our skills as butlers \Nto the utmost to serve Miss Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the unlikely event that my service \Nis less satisfactory than the boy's,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will leave the estate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.84,0:07:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.76,0:07:50.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will compete with all my might, \Nso as not to insult the Head Butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And thus, the serve-the-Miss match began.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, do you know what the most essential \Nskill is for a butler to have?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, like starting out hated,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.43,0:08:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but being thought of as a nice \Nperson by the final episode?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or swapping places with \None's mistress by chance
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and ending up solving the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be inspired enough to \Nanticipate what's to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need the ability to \Nread multiple steps ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to anticipate what your mistress desires!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the nobility, the morning \Nbegins with tea upon waking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.62,0:08:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, if it's that, I already prepared it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is ready, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.67,0:08:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.29,0:08:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In England, the land of butlers, \Nthis is a duty that is so important
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that there is a role specially \Ndedicated to making tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do not even know how to \Nproperly make tea, you are no butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.52,0:08:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are technically tea bags made for \Nthe British Royal Household, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.08,0:08:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! That sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemon or cream? Which would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.54,0:09:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen here! Back in England, there \Nis no such thing as lemon tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only milk tea exquisitely \Nprepared by the butler
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.46,0:09:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,serves to bolster the start of every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.72,0:09:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go with lemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lemon tea you made is good, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.50,0:09:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi, please try to go a little easy on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.94,0:09:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just wrong. Just wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are going to school today, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.40,0:09:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, because it would be mean \Nto mess with Klaus too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.95,0:09:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.19,0:09:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may not look it, but \NKlaus and I go way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that we know each other well
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is precisely what makes \Nit worth messing with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Right now, I can get two \Nextra pieces with the bucket!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it comes with nuggets to boot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:10:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wonder if they ran out of chicken...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like he didn't \Nfollow us all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.75,0:10:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's a piece of finely \Npolished silverware!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the symbol of a first-rate butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.08,0:10:30.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Zvaaaaam!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy! I have quit being a human being!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're a Sanzenin household butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "butler" comes from one \Nwho oversees the wine collection,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a permutation of "bouteillier"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.88,0:10:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wine! Vintage wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.07,0:10:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Violet Overdrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.83,0:10:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bordeaux! Burgundy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no wine for a drunkard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kraaaash!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.76,0:11:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're both gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On sunny days like this, \Nplaying hooky is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's even more relaxing when I think \Nof how everyone else is studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if only we had a butler to make \Nus some tea, it would be perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sunlight Yellow Overdrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Switching places?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Negoro Butler Ninja Skill, the \NSwitching Places Technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was an unexpected nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My chronic back problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That's Nagi's head butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for a perch.\N({\u1}To{\u0}mari-gi o sagashite ima{\u1}su{\u0}.)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bittersweet memory.\N({\u1}Su{\u0}ppai omoide da{\u1}ze{\u0}.)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the?! Holy cow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is super first rate cake and tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Much appreciated!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you my life, so I \Nwanted you to enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! Let's dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:14.69,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Thank you," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:17.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A butler is his mistress's shadow,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:21.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but deep inside, he is always waiting \Nfor that one word of thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is better than the ones from \Nthe shop by the train station!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this tea has been poured exquisitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katsy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.08,0:12:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a really good reason for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about any of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Treat me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on Earth are you going on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.14,0:12:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Play dumb, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got vintage stuff, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.29,0:12:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukiji, you seem to be out for blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis! What are you doing being \Nso violent towards the elderly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The elderly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he came falling \Nout of the sky just earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.46,0:12:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a grandpa, and who knows when \Nsomething might happen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,RIP.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.26,0:13:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mr. Klaus?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.32,0:13:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how far could they have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Klaus has probably recovered by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Here I was wondering who you might be,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if it isn't the renowned \NMr. Klaus of the butler world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by your appearance, you are \Na butler of the Ohkouchi household.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Himuro Saeki.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Heave-ho! Heave-ho! Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is Little Master Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will pretend I did not hear that last part.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Butlers have long considered it an honor
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to be called by their master's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.80,0:13:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are an Ohkouchi butler and \Nyou do not even know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, I had no idea, Himuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Master! Petals!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you would cite an Edwardian \Ncustom in our Heisei Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.51,0:13:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is so difficult to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sight of a formerly great \Nbutler in his declining years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is sad that even as you \Nhave grown feeble with age,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.73,0:14:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you still cling to your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That was awesome, Himuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.70,0:14:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With reflexes like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will not be able to protect your \Nmistress in her time of need, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you should retire and \Nthink about living your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are young, Ohkouchi butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am my mistress's shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadows never have their own \Nprivate lives to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I see that I can no longer \Nbe of use to my mistress,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all that is left is for me \Nto merely disappear quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.77,0:14:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he just found his resolve to step down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.56,0:14:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there no way for us \Nto keep Mr. Klaus here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We do have a trump card for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:12.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it will require \Nyou to lend a helping body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.33,0:15:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please. That would \Nbe "lend a helping {\i1}hand{\i0}".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I have such fond memories of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My life's purpose was to be \Nwith the Sanzenin household
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and to live out my days here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what the young Ohkouchi \Nbutler said had some merit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it is high time I ended this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.41,0:15:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I have met you somewhere before!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.03,0:16:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the sweet lady I saw in the garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was a good idea, if I do say so myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate's unique allure when dressed \Nin women's clothes would be effective
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even in the gay town of Ni-chome, Shinjuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Mr. Klaus will surely \Nfind comfort in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayasaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayasaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's H-H-H-Hermione!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Hermione!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.70,0:16:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fantastic name! Like the \Nname of someone who can use magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.56,0:16:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I am a goddess, who \Nlives in the estate's Yashagaike Pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! I knew that you could \Nnot be an ordinary lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Klaus,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.00,0:16:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been watching you all this \Ntime from the bottom of the pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.35,0:16:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Have you really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must not quit being the head butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are still far too young for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.34,0:17:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have grown weak with old age and \Neven my hair is completely white.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a fine gentleman with graying hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.26,0:17:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I am, aren't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get that a lot at the adult \Nsocial club in Ikebukuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you will no longer say \Nyou will retire, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But lately, I can barely lift my \Narms because of my old shoulders...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.01,0:17:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're just a little \Nstiff, that's all. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at how stiff you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stiff!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do my upper and lower back as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there. Right there. That's the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.21,0:17:45.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please hurry up and get convinced!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:48.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You difficult bow-tied old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is Klaus talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Further that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we cannot go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Time for a tasty treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hermione, th-the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think I have grown senile \Nenough to be seeing things...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.33,0:18:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It backfired...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This tiger again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Brazil Overseas Trips for Seniors
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.30,0:18:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tama, don't tell me you did \Nthis for a female tiger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've fallen in love with that female tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a tiger, so I can't \Nget to Brazil all on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.32,0:18:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so you used Mr. Klaus?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go to the plantation in Brazil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go. You want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just whispered that to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.65,0:18:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.66,0:18:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no tigers in Brazil!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.79,0:18:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I tell Mr. Klaus that \Nhis dream about Brazil
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.22,0:19:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wasn't the product of his subconscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that it was Tama's underhanded plot...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forgotten that no one \Nknows that Tama can talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:19:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.81,0:20:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the flower language for this flower?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.41,0:20:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, it is loyalty to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.37,0:20:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.52,0:20:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I just made it so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.77,0:20:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It no longer matters, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing that I can do \Nthat you are not capable of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.87,0:20:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This morning's Butler \NEconomy Marketing Journal
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.74,0:20:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is soaked from the morning dew!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't read the stock market news!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.43,0:20:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head Butler.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have yet to teach me \Nhow to iron the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't even iron the newspaper, \Nthe winner of the match is Klaus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:20:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Klaus!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.44,0:21:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.34,0:21:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A good temperature!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Mr. Klaus has completely recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.72,0:21:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We owe it all to you, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He may not be much, but he is a \Npart of the Sanzenin household.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would not wake up feeling \Ngood if I had driven him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.18,0:21:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go make some lemon tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.08,0:21:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.85,0:21:47.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time, they will not fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:50.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but instead, aim to coexist \Nwith small animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Waratte lun-lun-lun\NSmile lun-lun-lun
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.25,0:21:58.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lala-lun-lun-lulu naita hi mo\NLala-lun-lun-lulu even on a day I've cried
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:03.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sawagu kaze ni yureru egao kokoro hareteku\NA smile wavers in the wind and clears my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.71,0:22:06.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyou mo lun-lun-lun mawarun-lun-lulu\NToday again lun-lun-lun turning lun-lun-lulu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.92,0:22:18.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiyou no shita de kimi to odoru kimagure na dansu\NA whimsical dance with you under the sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:26.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nanige-naku sashi-dasu te ni mitorete\NRiveted by the hand you've casually offered
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.44,0:22:32.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugi no kotoba maigo ni natchau no\NMy next words become lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.78,0:22:37.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Otonabite tsutsumi-komu manazashi ni\NThe mature gaze that envelopes me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.91,0:22:42.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuyogari wasurete-yuku\NMakes me forget my bravado
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.29,0:22:49.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sotto furetete nemurenai yoru no nagai toki mo\NKeep that soft touch on long sleepless nights
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:54.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yume kara sameta bakari no hoho ni mo\NAnd on my cheek, just awakened from a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.43,0:22:56.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lun-lun-lun\NLun-lun-lun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:23:00.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lala-lun-lun-lulu tsun to shita\NLala-lun-lun-lulu that hoity profile
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.73,0:23:05.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yokogao hora atto iu ma waratteru desho?\NLook, there's a smile there already, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:09.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora to lun-lun-lun mawarun-lun-lulu\NWith the sky lun-lun-lun turning lun-lun-lulu
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.11,0:23:13.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi ga fukasu kaze no naka\NIn a breeze of your making
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.53,0:23:20.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Odoru hidamari no dansu\NA dance in a sunny spot
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.07,0:23:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(328.862,89.8)}Wataru & Saki's
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru and...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.14,0:23:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saki's...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:29.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.85,0:23:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.81,0:23:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the sunny smile and the boyish charm,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.95,0:23:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the manager of Rental Video \NTachibana, Wataru Tachibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.64,0:23:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I help take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.40,0:23:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the maid, Saki Kijima.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.78,0:23:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the image song is ready to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.67,0:23:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe we should make some \Npromotional merchandise!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.04,0:23:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think would sell well?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a rare glimpse \Nat Rental Video Tachibana's
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.95,0:23:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,clutzy maid in a pleasingly \Nembarassing situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? You {\i1}have {\i0}been \Nattracting more customers, lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.31,0:23:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young sir, would you please stop it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.49,0:23:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.05,0:23:59.03,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,224)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.15,0:24:00.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, what kind of girl \Nwould you say is your type?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.06,0:24:12.08,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.22,0:24:01.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, good question...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.90,0:24:04.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I like normal girls the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.18,0:24:04.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Normal"?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.86,0:24:07.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure you'd understand, miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.72,0:24:12.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?! Do you think I \Ncan't become your ideal girl!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.14,0:24:13.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.69,0:24:16.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"I Want to Go Back to Being an Ordinary Girl,\N But Buy My Character Songs, Okay?"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.91,0:24:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Want to Go Back to Being an Ordinary Girl,\N But Buy My Character Songs, Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.17,0:24:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.61,0:24:19.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So, Hayate likes normal girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.52,0:24:22.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know the lion statues in \Nfront of certain apartment buildings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.92,0:24:25.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,are called "shiisa" in Okinawa?
